Cam::

She looked up at Kup and then to Windlord. "My mommy tld me not to 
let anything happen to the cubes. I gave you one and now you just 
want the others. I won't let that happen. I will keep the others 
safe, Jus as my mommy told me. The rest of the cubes are mine. MINE!"

She trasnformed into fox mode and ran past Kup and Windlord.  She ran 
into the airlock and got outside the quarintine rooms.  She stopped 
and jumped up on the console.  She pressed her paw to the button to 
lock the door. "Sorry, I have to leave now. I wanted to play longer. 
But I have to do what my mommy told me to do."

She looked at them through the glass, pain showe in her small 
optics. "I'm sorry."

With that, she ran down the hallway. She found a small hole in a vent 
cover and pushed her way through it.  In doind so, she left behind a 
small patch of bright red fur.
